{"tid":447523,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"每次忍屎，都係思考人生既好機會","createTime":"2017-10-25T11:10:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-28T10:09:35.000Z","uid":15935,"like":35,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"d6d19a0a314ebe88293e657d1a9eb06ba637d476","tid":447523,"uid":15935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T11:10:13.000Z","msg":"當你意識到個肚真係好撚痛，啲屎準備係屎眼爆出黎而附近又無廁所，個種絕望既感覺完全不亞於耶穌比人釘十字架等死咁...係搵廁所既途中，你開始思考哲學，包括苦難(屎眼就爆，點解用意識呃佢話唔痛)、自尊(瀨咗佢好唔好？會唔會比人聞到？)、距離同時間(想要商場廁所個陣又離佢咁撚柒遠)、萬惡既資本主義(啲鋪頭會唔會開私伙廁所比你一用？)、幸福(陣痛消失，比多十幾秒你搵)....人生真係好苦"},{"pid":"43e101eb5c133355a2445e7b2e7db73bd7cc0f21","tid":447523,"uid":11475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T11:12:05.000Z","msg":"Yes"},{"pid":"f8ec5c3d5ed3e9b0524b6642f6e1ee639683a4e6","tid":447523,"uid":119379,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T11:46:39.000Z","msg":"有次上堂仲有半個鐘落堂，我個肚個個時候先黎痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n本身諗住死忍，點知5分鐘後肚又唔痛，10分鐘後又黎痛，仲有15分鐘落堂，最後都係頭也不回衝去廁所<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e1ff793afedb7e877038a471f6d909bc331defd","tid":447523,"uid":15935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T20:40:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有次上堂仲有半個鐘落堂，我個肚個個時候先黎痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n本身諗住死忍，點知5分鐘後肚又唔痛，10分鐘後又黎痛，仲有15分鐘落堂，最後都係頭也不回衝去廁所<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n所以一開始痛個陣就唔應該死忍...因為愈忍既下場只會愈黎愈慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d595ec8486918c25a84dcbc8b9394ce8c4aa11d6","tid":447523,"uid":27416,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T20:43:49.000Z","msg":"巴士啱啱上高速先黎急係最好反思人生既時候"},{"pid":"c5dbd24b8d29e4bddacee1861b8c3763d4d41dc0","tid":447523,"uid":107157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T21:43:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴士啱啱上高速先黎急係最後反思人生既時候</blockquote>"},{"pid":"477c6ce2b4e862863fe394b09b4508c46bb180f8","tid":447523,"uid":2263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T21:50:07.000Z","msg":"便秘先係"},{"pid":"efc3768b32c86278cc0b4616f10b93e49cdd92bd","tid":447523,"uid":74712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T23:03:03.000Z","msg":"樓主搵到廁所未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c37c537dd42aab406c092bcef9d865ccb4dc35fd","tid":447523,"uid":1562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T23:19:10.000Z","msg":"至撚憎忍屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"866045dd90730a6f2dca6abd360f4b67f03eedc1","tid":447523,"uid":1562,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T23:22:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>至撚憎忍屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n所以自己會研究左<br />\n平時返工返學嘅地方<br />\n會途經嘅地方嘅公廁位置同質素<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85981d51ee87ed0594504c3fd14a8a65237a086f","tid":447523,"uid":105445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T23:26:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>至撚憎忍屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n所以自己會研究左<br />\n平時返工返學嘅地方<br />\n會途經嘅地方嘅公廁位置同質素<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n所以我最撚憎啲仆街去廁格痾尿 痾到一地都係同埋唔揭廁板<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢地冇諗過自己都會有一天突然急屎要去公廁的時候<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0110a57f62bd79f081bc48fc073a469189985eec","tid":447523,"uid":144201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T23:27:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>至撚憎忍屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n所以自己會研究左<br />\n平時返工返學嘅地方<br />\n會途經嘅地方嘅公廁位置同質素<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n啱呀"},{"pid":"aef39fb6842a721ed46f9459a03ebe7a784f9e5c","tid":447523,"uid":86893,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T23:33:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/26/073259_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F26%2F073259_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=27b19dfd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n古人早就知道<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea953deb0d86845ed3d525e64dbd9463ae6a1438","tid":447523,"uid":70205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T23:36:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴士啱啱上高速先黎急係最好反思人生既時候</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n所以我避免坐巴士"},{"pid":"ed6b6bf53855bc08f0adacce7692af5816143dd4","tid":447523,"uid":15935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T04:36:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主搵到廁所未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n搵到廁所享受緊個陣先開post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c39f8352431c32bd4dae3134e8b6e959f39b47ca","tid":447523,"uid":15935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T17:49:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/26/073259_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F26%2F073259_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=27b19dfd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n古人早就知道<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n仲要除晒衫衫褲褲先去屙屎咁識嘆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cd4c00195ee6a2426eea58b2ceb0958c726777a","tid":447523,"uid":55249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T21:47:49.000Z","msg":"忍屎唔能夠分心去思考 否則會賴屎"},{"pid":"89ece4b42cb8ea3c40a4831ee82fe3c226ff8045","tid":447523,"uid":15935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T10:09:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>忍屎唔能夠分心去思考 否則會賴屎</blockquote><br />\n個個moment真係想死撚咗佢就算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}